{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B41ThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProviderC","title":"OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class"},"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of quantity input","type":"text"}]},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSQuantityInput"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeQuantityInputComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"QuantityInputComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"e